form.current-chamber: In the House of Representatives, U. S.,
form.official-title: Ranking a Member on a certain standing committee of the House of Representatives.

section.text: That the following named Member be, and is hereby, ranked on the following standing committee of the House of Representatives:

committee-appointment-paragraph.text: Ms. Maloy (to rank immediately after Mr. Strong).
